library(cluster)
library(jpeg)
library(grid)
pic <- readJPEG("C:/Users/jslaight/Documents/UNC/Classes/Spring 2020/STOR 320/wedding.jpg")
pic[,, 1] <- 0
pic[,, 2] <- 0
grid.raster(pic)

pic <- readJPEG("C:/Users/jslaight/Documents/UNC/Classes/Spring 2020/STOR 320/wedding.jpg")
bluepic <- pic[,,3]
m <- prcomp(bluepic, scale. = T)
pca_approx <- function(data, pca_loadings, d){
  pca_loadings <- pca_loadings[, 1:d]
  out <- (data %*% pca_loadings) %*% t(pca_loadings)
}
blueout <- pca_approx(bluepic, m$rotation, 100)
blueout <- (blueout - min(blueout)) / max(blueout - min(blueout))
grid.raster(as.raster(blueout))
